    "Canonical classification algorithms, including Support Vector Machines (SVM) (Cristianini and Shawe-Taylor, 2000; Awad et al., 2015), AdaBoost ensemble learning frameworks (Freund et al., 1999), and Deformable Part-based Model (DPM) networks (Viola and Jones, 2001), represent pivotal computational paradigms employed in this sophisticated classificatory process."
